{"tid":462654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冷血情婦】泰女被已婚韓男搞大肚 遭拋棄後掟初生兒落街","createTime":"2017-11-08T17:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T05:37:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65cde02c10bbf0f82196f1ebc9d539d9b1757bf8","tid":462654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171108/large/1510117912_d5ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171108%2Flarge%2F1510117912_d5ac.jpg&h=70054fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國芭堤雅一名20歲女子搭上到當地工作的南韓已婚工程師，甘做情婦長達兩年，未料女子懷孕後立即遭工程師拋棄，結果她狠心將初生親兒擲落樓殺害。<br />\n<br />\n20歲的萘茶諾搭上40歲金姓工程師，雖然明知對方在南韓已有妻室，但萘茶諾自18歲起就甘做情婦。兩年來金先生偶爾找萘茶諾，直到得知她懷孕8個多月後，就想盡辦法疏遠她，近日更提出分手，說要回南韓與妻子生活，令萘茶諾的心傷透。<br />\n住在芭堤雅一座大宅的萘茶諾周一去洗手間時，突然誕下健康的兒子，但萘茶諾一想到金先生的背叛及拋棄，加上自己又沒經濟能力養大孩子，於是狠心將他放入膠袋並拋落樓。一位在4樓裝窗簾的師傅，留意到有膠袋從眼前閃過墮落地面，於是探頭查看，駭然發現袋中有一名初生嬰兒，馬上報警求助。<br />\n男嬰腦漿塗地當場慘死，萘茶諾被捕時滿不在乎，表現得一點也不傷心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171108/57432121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57432121&d=gXDHcVhkjiWzOhIxOqKrkv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c74d9d28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57432121&h=337f3a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171108/57432121</a>"},{"pid":"b926181aa505ff48854336690a92ff36ac3d27e6","tid":462654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9f59557f6b6963895aaf94afb221631e765f89","tid":462654,"uid":124169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:57:58.000Z"